HEADWORD: Queen-post
<hw>Queen"-post`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <mark>[Arch.]</mark>
<def>One of two suspending posts in a roof truss, or other framed truss
of similar form. See <er>King-post</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

